-----------------------------
In both Procedures and TDE Oriented Output:
 
- Replace http:// with hxxp:// and https:// with hxxps://.
- Replace dots in domains and IPs with [.] (e.g., example.com → example[.]com, 1.2.3.4 → 1[.]2[.]3[.]4).
 
No live URLs, domains, or IPs
[01-07-2026 21:21] CTI: anywhere in the tables.
 
